    "description": "<strong>《Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun 2》是复古第一人称射击游戏《Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun》的快节奏凶残续作。</strong><br><br>故事紧接着《Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun》的结尾展开，你在分支结构的单人战役中前往新的地点履行职责，体验黑暗残酷的 Warhammer 40,000 宇宙与快节奏第一人称射击游戏的完美融合。 <br><br><strong>扮演全新的冠军</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/a62e99269e80f26cffa9c665fc999ebd.poster.avif?t=1772218838\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/a62e99269e80f26cffa9c665fc999ebd.webm?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/a62e99269e80f26cffa9c665fc999ebd.mp4?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>两个可玩角色可供选择，各自拥有独特的能力、武器和玩法。<br><br>威势赫赫的肃卫老兵马鲁姆·凯多因净化异端而闻名，是一股主宰战斗的不屈之力。轻灵敏捷的战斗修女奈拉·维拉思则擅长快速掌控战场，所到之处，敌人尽皆焚为灰烬。<br><br><strong>探索全新的世界</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/229dc1c009649b65e04d17f5ba6ca57a.poster.avif?t=1772218838\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/229dc1c009649b65e04d17f5ba6ca57a.webm?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/229dc1c009649b65e04d17f5ba6ca57a.mp4?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>前往从未踏足的世界，消灭潜伏当地的敌人。从高耸入云的巢都到寸步难行的丛林沼泽，你需要克服各种环境中的险恶挑战来完成肩负的使命。<br><br><strong>血腥刺激的战斗</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/347ec25163b1ad4fdcf28bf5470653e8.poster.avif?t=1772218838\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/347ec25163b1ad4fdcf28bf5470653e8.webm?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/347ec25163b1ad4fdcf28bf5470653e8.mp4?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《Warhammer 40,000: Boltgun》的劲爆战斗的基础上再度升级，让你配备星际战士五花八门的危险武器，一往无前地投入荣耀的战斗之中。挥舞致命的链锯剑将敌人大卸八块，或是端起霰弹枪将其轰成血肉模糊的残渣！<br><br><strong>前所未有的敌人</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/ef2a139a108d4fc57d67d21e2e4e5dca.poster.avif?t=1772218838\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/ef2a139a108d4fc57d67d21e2e4e5dca.webm?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/ef2a139a108d4fc57d67d21e2e4e5dca.mp4?t=1772218838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的武器库不断提升，敌人也不甘示弱！凶残的放血者骑在恶魔巨兽上冲入战场，化身为近乎势不可挡的嗜血怪物！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115160/extras/5f482b700148cbc2419adadbcab1f248.webp?t=1772218838\" width=616 height=49 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>]两个可玩角色：</strong>扮演威势赫赫的马鲁姆·凯多或久经沙场的奈拉·维拉思，两个角色玩法各异。<br></li><li><strong>炸裂的第一人称射击玩法：</strong>在令人血脉偾张的战斗中大开杀戒。<br></li><li><strong>分支结构战役：</strong>通过战役选择自己的路线，每个分支包含独特的关卡。<br></li><li><strong>全新敌人：</strong>迎战来自不同派系的前所未见的敌人。<br></li><li><strong>全新武器：</strong>使用毁灭性的武器碾碎无穷无尽的异端敌潮。<br></li><li><strong>全新地点：</strong>探索多个新世界和生态环境。<br></li><li><strong>寻路向导：</strong>在战场上轻松穿行，始终处于战斗中心。<br></li><li><strong>还有更多精彩内容！</strong></li></ul>",
